      <title>漢堡王母公司餐廳品牌因需求強勁而超乎預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/burger-king-parent-restaurant-brands-tops-revenue-estimates-strong-demand-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受漢堡王門市需求復甦以及 Tim Hortons 連鎖店持續走強的推動，Restaurant Brands International 週二的季度業績超出了華爾街預期。]]></description>
